Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:41.88,oped,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}毫不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:46.42,oped,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}即便受傷 也要前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:48.80,oped,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}我多次被你激勵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:51.01,oped,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}可每當這時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:54.51,oped,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}卻又莫名地想要哭泣
